title: Tomorrow never knows/Mr.Children COVER by 藤野櫻子
author: SWEETLOVESICK

detail.Title: Tomorrow never knows/Mr.Children COVER by 藤野櫻子
detail.Description:
(English is written below)  
今回は、Mr.Childrenが1994年11月10日にリリースし、ドラマ『若者のすべて』主題歌で、最終的にCD売上276.6万枚を記録した大ヒット6枚目シングル「Tomorrow never knows」を歌わせて頂きました。


声に合わせてキーを原曲から+7にしたことで、楽器の演奏方法や音域が変わったため、全体の印象が違うように感じる方もいらっしゃると思いますが、気に入って頂けたら嬉しいです。


もしよければ「チャンネル登録」「高評価」そして周りの方への「シェア」をよろしくお願いします。
歌のリクエストもありましたら、コメント欄に書いてくださいね。


---------------
♪藤野櫻子『SWEETLOVESICK』のサブチャンネル『さっちゃん家』

***


This time I sang Mr. Children's 6th single "Tomorrow never knows" which was released on November 10, 1994.

This song was the theme song for the drama "All About the Young," and was a big hit single by Mr. Children, with final CD sales of 2,766,000 copies.

Since the key was changed from the original to +7 to suit my voice, the way the instruments sound and the range of the song changed, and some may feel that the overall impression is different, but I hope you will like it.



If you like it, please "subscribe", "rate highly", and "share" with others.
If you have any song requests, please write them in the comment section.

This English is written using translation software.Please forgive any mistakes in English.
I would be very happy if you could write your thoughts on this song in the comments section.
